name: Blue Genesis Thread
description: The Mackay Glass chaotic differential equation was solved in three dimensions, plotted in 3D, scaled, and rotated.  Everything was done in R.  The color palette - inspired by Picasso's Blue Period, equation parameters, and plotting parameters were all optimized to create the most intriguing image as possible. 10,000 by 6,500 pixels. This is my HEN genesis piece.
